.TH SHAUGHVOS-INIT-SOFTWARE 1 "April 2026" "shaughvOS" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
shaughvos-init-software \- (re)install all bundled shaughvOS software
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B sudo shaughvos-init-software
.SH DESCRIPTION
Installs or reinstalls all software bundled with shaughvOS: QubeTX diagnostic tools (TR-300, ND-300, SD-300, SpeedQX), Node.js, npm, Claude Code CLI, and Firefox ESR.
.PP
Safe to re-run at any time. Skips software that is already installed. Requires network connectivity.
.SH SOFTWARE INSTALLED
.TP
.B Node.js + npm
JavaScript runtime and package manager (via apt).
.TP
.B Claude Code CLI
AI coding assistant (via claude.ai installer).
.TP
.B TR-300
Machine report tool \(em CPU, memory, disk, network overview.
.TP
.B ND-300 + SpeedQX
Network diagnostics and quad-provider speed test.
.TP
.B SD-300
Real-time interactive system diagnostics TUI.
.TP
.B Firefox ESR
Web browser (via apt).
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
0
All software installed successfully.
.TP
1
Network connectivity check failed, or one or more installs failed.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR tr300 (1),
.BR nd300 (1),
.BR sd300 (1),
.BR shaughvos-software (1)
